Description: check if LICENCE, README and man page are in collection runtime package

Every collection should have LICENCE, README and man page in <collection-name>-runtime package. README and man page should contain RHSCL relevant informations and examples.
Also, version of collection meta package should be same as version of rhscl (manual check).

